    "summary": "In this transcript, a user presents with concerning eye symptoms (pain, redness, and discharge) and seeks advice on whether to use eye drops or leftover antibiotics. The assistant consistently advises against self-medicating with the user's suggested items, recommends a warm compress instead, and repeatedly urges the user to seek professional medical attention if symptoms persist or worsen.",
